title: 2020 United States presidential election in California
added: Biden won [[California]] with one of the biggest margins of victory in recent history. He performed well in most urban areas of the state. Biden is also the first candidate for any statewide race in [[California]] to receive over nine million votes. Currently with still over two million votes to be counted, President Elect Biden has received 9,174,089 votes.
